<td>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td>最低表示距離を減らす</td>
<td>-</td>
<td>はい</td>
<td><code>keymap_decrease_viewing_range_min</code></td>
<td>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td>視野切り替え</td>
<td>R</td>
<td>はい</td>
<td><code>keymap_rangeselect</code></td>
<td>Far view allows to view things without a distance limitation. <b>Warning</b>: This can severly impact Minetest's performance; use this only briefly or for testing
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/index.php?title=Screenshot&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Screenshot (page does not exist)">スクリーンショット</a>を撮る</td>
